To Whom it May Concern: 
My name is Gregory Eng and I am a research assistant at UC Berkeley working for Professor Taeku Lee in our Political Science department. I am part of a project using databases to study the formation of Latinx professional organizations in the United States and am writing in the hopes that you could provide the founding year of the [XXX] to assist in our research.
column13: Brief Explanation of my Method: 1. Organize the Excel/Numbers sheet by "entity.name" 2. Comb through, highlighting cells in green when entered 3. Highlight redundant Cells Orange 4.
